sharedRegions.interfaces

  • Packages that use sharedRegions.interfaces 
    Package Description
    commonStructures
    Estuturas comuns à versão distribuída do problema do Restaurante.
    entities
    Entidades que participam no Problema do Restaurante.
    logging
    COntrução do ficheiro de log.
    sharedRegions.bar
    Contains the implementations related to the Bar, such as: BarStub - The stub provided to each entity who communicates with the Bar. RestaurantBar - the actual implementation of the Bar. RestaurantBarInterface - interface that's going to be provided to the ClientProxy in the Bar Server.
    sharedRegions.table
    Contains the implementations related to the Table, such as: TableStub - The stub provided to each entity who communicates with the Table. RestaurantTable - the actual implementation of the Table. RestaurantTableInterface - interface that's going to be provided to the ClientProxy in the Table Server.
